    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80c8-bdaa-c473f87ec325",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The apper explores the group formation problem using 3 constraints: inter-homogeneity, intra-heterogeneity and empathy. Optimization is done using a Genetic Algorithm. Comparison wtih 3 baselines on computastional terms and in a real setting against random and self-organized methods. In both, the proposed method showed potential.",
